<h1>Edit Wiki</h1>
 
 <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-4">
     <p>Guidelines for Wiki</p>
     <ul>
       <li>Please give concise title to your wiki. And elaborate more in the body.</li>
       <li>If your a standard user, your wiki can be publicly visible to all users.</li>
       <li>Graduate to Premium user if you want to have private wikis.</li>
       <li>Only Admin has the right to delete your wiki.</li>
     </ul>
   </div>
   <div class="col-md-8">
     <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { wiki: @wiki } %>
   </div>
 </div>